description.displayText: You definitely want Elizabeth to keep your children!  My girls think Miss Elizabeth is part of the family.  If you are looking for someone who will follow your care instructions to the letter and is creative when coming up with games and activities, she is the sitter for you.  She is game for meal prep, homework help, and whatever else you need for your children while you're away.  Your children will LOVE her and won't ever want you to hire anyone else again!
